Package: scArch
Type: Package
Title: Inferring metacells for cell state representation in single-cell data 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Botao Fa
Maintainer: Botao Fa <fabotao@xjtu.edu.cn>
Description: With increasing numbers of cells sequenced, find all the subtle cell states 
    is of high importance. CellUnit is an unsupervised, graph-based algorithm that 
    aggregates cells into compact metacells based on cell condensation and recursive splitting 
    with curated termination criteria.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.0), 
    Seurat (>= 4.0.2), 
    lsa (>= 0.73.3), 
    dbscan, 
    SeuratObject, 
    fastICA (>= 1.2.2),
    stats,
    utils
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
